Package: RZigZag
Type: Package
Title: Zig-Zag Sampler
Version: 0.2.0
Date: 2019-03-21
Author: Joris Bierkens
Maintainer: Joris Bierkens <joris.bierkens@tudelft.nl>
Description: Implements the Zig-Zag algorithm (Bierkens, Fearnhead, Roberts, 2016) <arXiv:1607.03188> applied to e.g. Gaussian target distributions, Bayesian logistic regression, and Bouncy Particle Sampler for a Gaussian target.
